sep.gaia.resources.tiles2d

Class TileQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.resources.Query
      • sep.gaia.resources.tiles2d.TileQuery

  • public class TileQuery
extends Query
    TileQuery is for requesting TileResource objects. Each TileQuery contains a Collection of TileResource (dummys).
    Author:
    Johannes Bauer

        resource - The dummies, specifying the coordinates and zoom of the tiles to load. They will be modified by the loader.
